Package: UltraGBIF
Title: An Ultrafast and User-friendly R Package to Parse and Merge Enormous GBIF Occurrence Records
Version: 3.0.1
Date: 2025-10-04
Type: Package
Maintainer: Yuxuan Wang <wyx1743@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Yuxuan", "Wang", email = "wyx1743@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-7817-748X"))
Description: GBIF hosts over 3 billion occurrence records. However, processing massive records typically involves lots of workflows and time, posing significant challenges for researchers. To address these limitations, we present UltraGBIF, an ultrafast and user-friendly R package to parse and merge enormous GBIF occurrence records.
